{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Phew! Nanami won!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Nanami dashes onto the stage ahead of you and turns to look at you smugly.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I'm still quick on my feet even if Power couldn't enter the maze!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I'm so happy... What an unexpectedly fun experience humans created!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami loves humans so much! And you're my favorite human, obviously, Commandant!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Nanami would love to go through this maze once more... noâ€”many times more with you!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'You want to do it again?', 3: '14', 4: "Won't you get bored?", 5: '16'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Of course! Let's go!", 4: '1'}
{2: "Won't you get bored, Nanami?", 3: '16'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "That's impossible! Nanami will make sure each experience feels different as long as we're together!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Hm... We can turn the paths of the maze into flumes! Or we can send some mechanoids in there as randomized traps!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'We can even...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Picturing what Nanami described, you find the maze before you suddenly become scarier.'}
{3: "Nanami continues to come up with more grand plans, so you try to put a stop to it before it's too late."}
{2: 'I think this is perfect already.', 3: '24'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "It's perfect? Are you sure you don't want to try some of Nanami's suggestions?", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm sure.", 3: '27', 4: 'We can try some if we have time in the future.', 5: '31'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Sigh. Fine.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You're right. What's important is the time I spend with you, Commandant, not the shape of the maze...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I know you're tempted, Commandant!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "I promise you I'll make an excellent and exciting giant maze!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Let's play this one again, then! I didn't get a good look at the contraption there!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'After all, I got to spend some time with you for once, Commandant!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She looks at you expectantly, seemingly waiting for your answer.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Yeah! The grand adventure of Nanami and Commandant through the maze begins now!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'With your permission, Nanami cheerfully grabs you outside and back to the entrance...'}
